Package: E3ExpressionShiny
Title: Shiny Explorer for E3 PROTAC Expression and Source-First Resource Data
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peter", "Thorpe", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "p.thorpe@dundee.ac.uk")
    )
Description: A modular Shiny application for querying and visualising
    Expression Atlas-derived expression data and the source-first E3 PROTAC
    Parquet/DuckDB resource rebuilt from inherited project files. The
    application uses DuckDB-backed bounded queries and is intended to remain
    extensible for E3 ligase, ligandability, literature, GO, sequence,
    Orthofinder and structural-conservation modules.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
